Description:
5 PRIVATE ACRES TO CREATE YOUR OWN PARADISE!
This 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with in ground pool, situated on 5 peaceful acres within minutes of Cockatoo is just waiting for a family to make it their own. Absolute privacy is assured in this spacious ranch style home featuring 4 spacious bedrooms with built in robes at one end of the home, one with an ensuite & a large Master with built in robes & ensuite effect bathroom at the other. The Master opens onto the generous formal lounge with a huge OFP, perfect for entertaining on those chilly winter nights. There is a 2nd living area, adjacent to the open plan country kitchen & a 3rd living area/rumpus room, giving all the family their own space & room to relax & entertain. Outside this low maintenance brick home has verandahs all round, a double lock up garage, established gardens, pony paddock & the private in ground pool, all located on 5 fully fenced acres. Your comfortable, private, family home awaits all you need bring is the vision.

Description:
Beautifully Presented with Unique Character and Charm
Beautifully styled inside and out, this immaculate 4-bedroom weatherboard home reflects a graceful design and an effortless lifestyle. It's perfectly positioned at the end of a no through road,
with a short stroll to the town, parklands and schools.
A truly unique property offering vaulted/cathedral ceilings, polished timber flooring and character features throughout.
Surrounded by low maintenance private gardens, the residence is double storey with a stylish clever floorplan. The ground floor offers two bedrooms and open plan living, incorporating a sunken living area with slow combustion heating, which leads out into the garden entertaining area. The generous well appointed timber kitchen offers ample storage and bench space with the meals/dining room overlooking the living area. The second level offers two generous bedrooms, the main bedroom with a walk in robe and its own private balcony, a recently renovated family bathroom to accommodate both bedrooms upstairs.
Other inclusions are, upstairs attic, gas ducted heating, combustion fireplace, reverse cycle air conditioning, off street parking.
Set on a private, cleared landscaped block with manicured lawns for all year round entertaining, including a brick bar-b-que area for your enjoyment.
This haven is what dreams are made of and is perfect for those wanting a stunning home in a peaceful and quiet location.
Give Chris 0428 643 917 or Verica 0402 012 499 a call now to book your appointment

Description:
ELEGANT, COMFORTABLE & SPACIOUS FAMILY HOME !
This large family home, on just under three quarters of an acre oozes warmth & character with exposed timber walls & ceilings & feature brickwork throughout. Featuring 4 bedrooms & 3 living ares this home has room for the whole family to have their own space. The white timber country kitchen is the hub of the home & features a dishwasher, large pantry & breakfast bar overlooking the family meals area. The family room is warmed by a toasty wood heater whilst the home also has zoned GDH for added convenience & comfort. The formal dining room creates the perfect environment for an evening with friends, & when dinner is finished move the gathering into the formal lounge with an ambient open fire place. At the end of the home there is a further living area, perfect for the kids. All bedrooms are generous in size, three with built in robes & the Master with walk in robe & ensuite. Outside there is a double carport, cubby, shed, a full sized tennis court, a small pony paddock & a fully fenced rear yard - offering plenty of flat land that could easily be transformed for a myriad of uses. This is a charming, family sized home that needs to be seen to be appreciated. Call to arrange a private inspection today!

Description:
Huge Shed For The Tradies...Immaculate Home For The Ladies!
This property offers something for everybody & is a haven for the tradies with a huge 12 x 6 garage with ample lighting & power outlets & comes complete with a pot belly stove!
The stylish, immaculately presented home features 3 bedrooms, including large master with ensuite & WIR, family bathroom & large laundry with plenty of storage space.
The kitchen in central to the home incorporates stainless steel appliances & large fridge cavity. The adjoining dining area & living room features a large open fire place & split system air con plus there is GDH throughout. Outside offers a gazebo surrounded by beautiful tranquil gardens along with sealed road access and a freshly sealed driveway leading to the huge garage. Only a short 6 km drive to Emerald, the home is also within walking distance to the Cockatoo shops, Reserve and Primary School.

Description:
FAMILY HOME IN PEACEFUL COURT LOCATION!
Situated on approximately three quarters of an acre minutes from Cockatoo, the Primary School & public transport, this 3 bedroom family home has the added bonus of a huge double lock up garage/workshop with concrete floor, kitchenette, enclosed office, power & its own wood heater. The home takes advantage of the morning sun to warm the living area & kitchen/ meals area whilst it has the convenience of mains GDH throughout. The functional kitchen features a 900mm S/S free standing oven, S/S dishwasher, heaps of cupboard space & a breakfast bar overlooking the meals area. All three bedrooms have built in robes, the master with floor to ceiling windows & ensuite effect to the main bathroom. Outside the home has an elevated, bush outlook, a gravel drive, a huge garage/workshop, a garden shed, mains gas & water & a further studio, perfect for the home based business or potential teenage accommodation. Call today to arrange a private inspection of this comfortable & private family home.

Description:
SIMPLY IRRESISTABLE
If you love the indoor and outdoor living then this one is for you. Immaculately presented and close to facilities yet privately located on 1454
m2 (approx.),this beautiful and lovingly maintained family home has a secure yard with well established gardens. Comfortable and affordable 'hills living' can be yours right here with all the right ingredients that you ever wanted. On offer is 3 good-sized robed bedrooms, master with full ensuite, study nook, timber galley style kitchen with dishwasher, separate meals area which leads to the alfresco courtyard and 'L' shaped lounge.
Special features include reverse cycle air conditioning, gas heater and quality 'Scandia' wood heater, large garage/workshop ideal for the handyperson, plus additional parking spaces. Families will have no problems finding their feet in this charming warm family home with such a prized position. Walking distance to schools and sporting facilities.
Look now before it's too late!

Description:
NEAT, FULLY RENOVATED 3 BEDROOM HOME!
This fully renovated home is the perfect opportunity to either move in with nothing to do or invest. From sunrise the living areas are filled with beautiful sunlight & the evenings can be spent relaxing on the deck & admiring the view. Fully painted inside & out with a new kitchen & all new floor & window coverings & light fittings, this home will suit the new home buyer. Featuring 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 with built in robes & the Master, with a walk in robe and ensuite, located off the formal lounge with huge OFP, this home is ideally zoned for comfortable family living. The sparkling new kitchen is functional & offers soft close doors & drawer & overlooks the light filled second living area with garden outlook. Outside there is a gravel drive, single carport, established lawns & gardens & a garden shed for all your tools. All this on over half an acre in a peaceful location just a few minutes from Cockatoo, the shops, primary school, local kinda & public transport.

Description:
NEAT 3 BEDROOM ON HALF AN ACRE 700M TO COCKATOO!
This tidy 3 bedroom western red cedar home is situated on half an acre on the high side of the road with an elevated outlook, only 700m from the Cockatoo Post Office, public transport, shops, take aways & restaurants. Featuring a circular drive for convenient access this home has established gardens out the front & a huge, terraced yard complete with fruit trees & a lockable garden shed out the back. The home offers 3 spacious bedrooms, all with built in robes & a large lounge room with slate floors, a pitched ceiling & a toasty wood heater for warmth. The well-appointed kitchen with breakfast bar & gas cooking overlooks the meals area with direct access to the rear deck, & there is a split system for added convenience. Add to this all mains services & this low maintenance gem is the ideal first home or investment opportunity.
CALL TO ARRANGE A PRIVATE INSPECTION TODAY!

Description:
BEAUTIFUL OUTLOOK WITH POSITION TO MATCH
This haven of a home on nearly 1 acre, is nestled on the peak of Paternoster Road offering some of the best valley and bay views the area has to offer.
Surrounded by impressive manicured gardens, the charming home features 3m ceilings, polished hardwood floors, lounge with wood heater, a timber kitchen with modern appliances and original wood stove, There are 3 bedrooms
as well as a true country bathroom with corrugated iron wall features and a timber toilet.
Connected to the house you will find a
studio/bungalow with its own bathroom and toilet that could be used as a
office or converted to self-contained accommodation.
Additional features including a solar heated pool, free range chicken pen, dog kennels, cat run and additional shedding, bore water, town water plus 58,000L of tank water, town gas also incorporating approved additional fire protection measures.

Description:
FAIRYTALE FAMILY HOME!
This beautifully maintained 5 bedroom family home is situated amongst half an acre of established gardens, just a few hundred metres from Cockatoo, the shops, post office, public transport & eateries. Freshly painted with a concrete drive, manicured gardens, a veggie patch & enormous undercover entertaining area, this home leaves nothing to do but relax & enjoy your surrounds. Inside offers a well-appointed kitchen opening onto a large family room with toasty wood heater whilst the home has mains GDH throughout for comfort & convenience. The Master Bedroom with walk in robe & ensuite sits adjacent to the second living area, whilst there are 2 further spacious bedrooms with built in robes on the ground floor at the other end of the home. At either end of the home there is a loft, offering maximum use of space & the perfect childrens bedrooms, study space or rumpus. Outside has the WOW factor, with a huge undercover entertaining area, cottage gardens, meandering paths & even a designer water feature, perfect for the largest of gatherings or a private & romantic dinner for 2. Add to all this a split system for the warmer days, a double lock up garage with remote & huge laundry & every box has been ticked.
INSPECTION WILL NOT DISAPPOINT. CALL TODAY!
